title: Blackmailers Contradict Each Other!
itunes:title: Blackmailers Contradict Each Other!
description:
The Young Turks attack the foremost journalists of our era!

Special guest: award winning journalist "BuzzSaw" Aaron Maté!

Phone calls from Joe Biden, Vladimir Putin, and Harrison Ford!

Featuring Stef Zamorano and Mike MacRae!
